  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>the Heights</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/19ff3786a1bb347bfb1b1bd8b1d78531.poster.avif?t=1720569897\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/19ff3786a1bb347bfb1b1bd8b1d78531.webm?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/19ff3786a1bb347bfb1b1bd8b1d78531.mp4?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready to Climb the Heights? </strong></h2><br>The heights is a timed first-person single-player action shooter. Play as a time travelling robot and ascend to the top floor to save the future. Shoot and climb to the top of the skyscraper whilst avoiding assured death. Solve puzzles to proceed to the next floor. Destroy all research and eliminate the CEO to save the future from doom. All this whilst on a time loop that resets you if you've outstayed your welcome.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fine Tuned First Person Shooting<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/ca3e34a1deb498c2db78143da280a535.poster.avif?t=1720569897\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/ca3e34a1deb498c2db78143da280a535.webm?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/ca3e34a1deb498c2db78143da280a535.mp4?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Teleporting Gizmo lets you reach new places you normally wouldn't be allowed<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/2249752f2e2d5f4e88b247084c70fab4.poster.avif?t=1720569897\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/2249752f2e2d5f4e88b247084c70fab4.webm?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/2249752f2e2d5f4e88b247084c70fab4.mp4?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fun and exciting timed loop<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/7220ef38e01364346a344325c91bcf16.poster.avif?t=1720569897\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/7220ef38e01364346a344325c91bcf16.webm?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/7220ef38e01364346a344325c91bcf16.mp4?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Fun and intuitive puzzles<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/b3a8a24b8c1190aa9ae2e3975b404ae6.avif?t=1720569897\" width=346 height=360 /></span><br></li><li>A fully voiced story<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/c7edf079bcb14785148a87219f7fec0f.poster.avif?t=1720569897\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/c7edf079bcb14785148a87219f7fec0f.webm?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238990/extras/c7edf079bcb14785148a87219f7fec0f.mp4?t=1720569897\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join the discord!</strong></h2><br>Join our community to ask questions, talk with the developer and voice actors, and leave suggestions for the future of the game.<br>",
